  "detailed_description": "When you died your body could not be found, a funeral was held and an empty casket was lowered into your grave. Many years later your soul has brought you back from death to finally find eternal rest.<br><br><strong>50+ Unlocks</strong><br>Advance your Necropolis and unlock game altering upgrades as you play. Discover Curses that influence your gameplay in different ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.poster.avif?t=1704751296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.webm?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.mp4?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong><br>Fight fearsome foes and gain unique abilities each time you venture through the cemetery. Uncover the mystery of your unending search and fight powerful bosses in the Catacombs.<br><br><strong>Deckbuilding and Upgrades</strong><br>Create the perfect graveyard and obtain powerful upgrades on your search for rest. Mix and match different upgrades each time you play to create unstoppable builds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.poster.avif?t=1704751296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.webm?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.mp4?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "When you died your body could not be found, a funeral was held and an empty casket was lowered into your grave. Many years later your soul has brought you back from death to finally find eternal rest.<br><br><strong>50+ Unlocks</strong><br>Advance your Necropolis and unlock game altering upgrades as you play. Discover Curses that influence your gameplay in different ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.poster.avif?t=1704751296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.webm?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/78244d96830ec58f3cc89ab7d71c93c3.mp4?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong><br>Fight fearsome foes and gain unique abilities each time you venture through the cemetery. Uncover the mystery of your unending search and fight powerful bosses in the Catacombs.<br><br><strong>Deckbuilding and Upgrades</strong><br>Create the perfect graveyard and obtain powerful upgrades on your search for rest. Mix and match different upgrades each time you play to create unstoppable builds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.poster.avif?t=1704751296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.webm?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338240/extras/f01e3ab523ef0cd52c57ae597fdbf855.mp4?t=1704751296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
